rComments: He's good tempered professor, however, his lectures are a little bit boring, and it is too easy to lose track because his voice is too calming...

Great guy. Lectures are a little boring but he makes the most of them. Tests are fair and marked fairly however he marks the group project very hard. You can do very well in his course simply by putting the work in.
Great prof for RSM219. He explains concepts well enough and tries to make the class interesting. Would definitely take another class by him.
The nicest and hottest professor I've ever had!
